org.knime.base.data.aggregation

Class AggregationMethods

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.base.data.aggregation.AggregationMethods
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AggregationFunctionProvider<AggregationMethod>

    public final class AggregationMethods
extends Object
implements AggregationFunctionProvider<AggregationMethod>
    Singleton that lists all available aggregation methods including helper methods to retrieve meaningful methods.

    Tobias Koetter, University of Konstanz
